{
  "text": "\u03c9. Subsequently, we minimize over \u03ba. Remark 6. The modeling and analysis framework presented in this paper also allows to include two other classes of quantizers, namely, logarithmic and 'zoom quantizers', as introduced in [CITATION_1] and [CITATION_2] , respectively. However, for the sake of brevity, we refer to van Loon et al. [2012] regarding details.",
